---
title: Italian Style Lamb Burgers with Sun-Dried Tomatoes, Pesto and Wedges
description: These Burgers with Wedges and Rocket are bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-sun-dried-tomato-lamb-burgers-782260d3-110d5c57.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/italian-sun-dried-tomato-lamb-burgers-5cae0483e3f3396cbc5e88d2-60696d88.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 775 kcal
  fat: 31 g
  saturated fat: 8 g
  carbohydrates: 94 g
  sugar: 12 g
  protein: 31 g
  sodium: 3 g
